{"title":"Northwave Revolution 2025 Review: A Stiffer, Sleeker, Upgrade","link":"https://bikerumor.com/northwave-revolution-2025/","date":1745325981000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-both--1536x864.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" alt=\"Northwave Revolution both\" /></p>\n<p>Northwave has been quietly cranking out solid road shoes for years, and the Revolution has always been a bit of an underdog in the brand’s lineup—stiff, sleek, and loaded with performance features without drawing too much attention away from the flagship <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/northwave-veloce-extreme-road-shoe-increase-your-watts/\">Veloce Extreme shoes</a>. The 2025 Northwave Revolution is here, and while it doesn’t reinvent the shoe, it refines it.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-insole--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-insole--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Northwave Revolution insole\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-insole--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-insole--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-insole--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-insole--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-insole--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-insole--2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-insole--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos: Jordan Villella/BikeRumor.com)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>After a few hundred miles in the new kicks, it’s clear this is a refined version of what already worked—better ventilation, a beefed-up carbon sole, and a fit system that lets you dial in the lockdown without overcooking the pressure. Let’s break it down.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-look-ing-at--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-look-ing-at--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Northwave Revolution look ing at\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-look-ing-at--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-look-ing-at--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-look-ing-at--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-look-ing-at--120x67.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-look-ing-at--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-look-ing-at--2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-look-ing-at--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>What’s New? More Evolution Than Revolution</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>At first glance, you’d be forgiven for thinking not much has changed. But step in, clip in, and give it a few hard efforts, and you’ll feel the upgrades doing their job in the background.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-logo--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-logo--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Northwave Revolution logo\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-logo--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-logo--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-logo--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-logo--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-logo--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-logo--2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-logo--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Northwave Revolution – <strong>Key Highlights:</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Morph Carbon 12 AAS Sole:</strong> The updated carbon platform gains stiffness without becoming a foot-numbing torture device. Northwave gives it a 12 out of 15 on their in-house stiffness scale, and I’d agree—it’s stiff enough for race day but still tolerable for big-mile weekends.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Dual SLW3 Dials:</strong> This is a significant upgrade. The dual-dial system replaces the previous single-dial setup, providing micro-adjustments across the entire foot. Tighten, loosen, fine-tune—it’s all intuitive and quick.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Revised Ventilation:</strong> A reworked mesh pattern enhances airflow at the front and along the sides. It’s subtle but effective, especially noticeable on sweltering rides.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Lower Stack Height:</strong> You feel a slightly closer connection to the pedals, which adds to the snappy, direct feel during sprints and climbs.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Price</strong>: $250.00</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Weight: </strong>295g/shoe size 42.5*<em> (Northwaves Flagship Veloce Extreme weighs 275g in the same size)</em><br /></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-header--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-header--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Northwave Revolution header\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-header--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-header--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-header--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-header--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-header--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-header--2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-header--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Fit: Wider Where It Matters</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Northwave continues its “comfort with performance” approach here. The toe box remains roomy compared to ultra-skinny Italian brands, which is a blessing on long days when feet swell. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-grippers--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-grippers--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Northwave Revolution grippers\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-grippers--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-grippers--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-grippers--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-grippers--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-grippers--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-grippers--2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-grippers--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The midfoot feels locked in, especially with the new dial setup, and the heel cup has just enough padding to prevent lift without going overboard.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-sinole-close--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1439\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-sinole-close--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Northwave Revolution sinole close\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-sinole-close--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-sinole-close--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-sinole-close--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-sinole-close--120x67.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-sinole-close--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-sinole-close--2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-sinole-close--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>That dual-dial system is the MVP—spread-out tension and a fit that can be tweaked mid-ride without breaking rhythm. Bonus points for the revised tongue that stays flat and pressure-free.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-inside--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-inside--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Northwave Revolution inside\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-inside--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-inside--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-inside--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-inside--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-inside--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-inside--2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-inside--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>On the Road: Efficient, Not Brutal</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This shoe’s not trying to out-stiff a full-on race slipper like the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/specialized-s-works-ares-2-road-cycling-race-shoe/\">S-Works Ares 2</a> or a DMT KRSL. Instead, it strikes a sweet balance—plenty stiff under load, but not so harsh you want to kick them off after 70 miles.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-bottoms--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-bottoms--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Northwave Revolution bottoms\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-bottoms--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-bottoms--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-bottoms--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-bottoms--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-bottoms--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-bottoms--2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-bottoms--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Out-of-the-saddle efforts felt more direct, with noticeably less sole flex than the outgoing version. Power transfer is clean and predictable, and paired with the lower stack height, you get a snappier, more connected ride feel. The updated, staggered grippers on the heel cup provide a nice, sunk-in feeling with a secure grip.  </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-cleats--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-cleats--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Northwave Revolution cleats\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-cleats--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-cleats--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-cleats--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-cleats--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-cleats--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-cleats--2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-cleats--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Breathability: Cool, Not Compromised</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The ventilation redesign is subtle, but it works. Hot, humid summer rides didn’t cook my feet, and airflow through the toe box was steady without compromising structure. And crucially, durability isn’t sacrificed—no fraying, delaminating, or scuffing after some solid abuse.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-dials-close-up-scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-dials-close-up-1536x864.webp\" alt=\"Northwave Revolution dials close up\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-dials-close-up-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-dials-close-up-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-dials-close-up-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-dials-close-up-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-dials-close-up-2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-dials-close-up-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-dials-scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-dials-1536x864.webp\" alt=\"Northwave Revolution dials\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-dials-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-dials-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-dials-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-dials-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-dials-2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-dials-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-toe-box--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-toe-box--1536x864.webp\" alt=\"Northwave Revolution toe box\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-toe-box--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-toe-box--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-toe-box--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-toe-box--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-toe-box--2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-toe-box--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Final Thoughts: Worth it</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you’re already a fan of the Revolution, the 2025 model brings meaningful improvements across the board. A better fit, better cooling, and better power delivery. It’s not a must-upgrade if your current pair still has life in it, but if you’re nearing retirement mileage, this one’s a no-brainer replacement.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-carbon--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-carbon--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Northwave Revolution carbon\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-carbon--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-carbon--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-carbon--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-carbon--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-carbon--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-carbon--2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-carbon--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>At $250, it’s also a killer value—especially when you’re staring down the barrel of $500+ for top-tier models. The Northwave Revolution 2025 strikes the perfect balance of performance for riders seeking race-day power without exceeding their race-season budget.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-weight--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-weight--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Northwave Revolution weight\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-weight--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-weight--297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-weight--1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-weight--120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-weight--768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Northwave-Revolution-weight--2048x1536.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s fast. It’s comfy. And it’s not trying to be something it’s not. A truly exceptional road shoe that continues to improve with every ride.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.northwave.com/en/bike/shoes/road/northwave-revolution-2025\">Northwave.com</a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/northwave-revolution-2025/\">Northwave Revolution 2025 Review: A Stiffer, Sleeker, Upgrade</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jordan Villella","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"f9966216cabf90d0a635374178ff96d0a44f7d4472f854de0653f03a675d80b3","category":"Cycling"}